{"tid":605757,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【愛情社會經濟學】做愛都會被人屈強姦 ? 從 MeToo 運動，淺談「性行為同意書」","createTime":"2018-03-26T02:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T19:16:34.000Z","uid":58377,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd41db05ae724a405a360e564f6916eb57631d4","tid":605757,"uid":58377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T02:59:08.000Z","msg":"<em>愛情社會經濟學 -- 以愛情既角度，談討社會經濟。</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://missethoreca.nl.s3-eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/app/uploads/2017/11/shutterstock_736146343-272x181-272x181.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmissethoreca.nl.s3-eu-central-1.amazonaws.com%2Fapp%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Fshutterstock_736146343-272x181-272x181.jpg&h=604d2342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「#MeToo」運動席捲全球 , 香港亦都因為呂麗瑤而掀起 MeToo 浪潮。犯咗性侵罪行既男人當然要拉 , 但同時 , 卻有女仔濫用 MeToo 去冤枉別人<br />\n<br />\n<strong>明明係自願既一夜情 , 但條女就冤枉人地強姦</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/128564/美容師遇情場騙子-報警稱遭強姦報復-認報假案被判社服100小時\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F128564%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%B9%E5%B8%AB%E9%81%87%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B4%E9%A8%99%E5%AD%90-%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%AD%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9-%E8%AA%8D%E5%A0%B1%E5%81%87%E6%A1%88%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%8D100%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA04S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=8f845c12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/128564/美容師遇情場騙子-報警稱遭強姦報復-認報假案被判社服100小時</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做愛都被人屈強姦 , 咁無良 , 有冇方法保障男士 ? <br />\n<br />\n最簡單既方法 , 就係做愛之前簽<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>「性行為同意書」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n扑野都要簽同意書 ? 一向做事小心既香港人都唔肯啦 , 更何況鬼佬 ? <br />\n<br />\n你錯啦 , 你以為歐洲人最提倡性自由 , 但其實第一個提出「性行為同意書」既 , 就係歐洲人"},{"pid":"9b9b6b0db4607c82776e35f67490d579e75cb892","tid":605757,"uid":58377,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:00:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">全球首創「性行為同意書」手機 App</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180114/1278112/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180114%2F1278112%2F&d=O3%2By7wO7X%2Bwwy%2FDqU%2FGA04S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=87ac0bfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180114%2F1278112%2F&h=c44edec5\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180114/1278112/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://allthatsinteresting.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/legalfling-screenshots.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fallthatsinteresting.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2Flegalfling-screenshots.jpg&h=1c10c07f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭既手機程式 LegalFling , 就以區塊鏈技術實現「性行為同意書」。雙方仲可以自訂「性行為條款」 , 例如 <strong>是否戴套</strong> , <strong>玩唔玩 SM</strong> 等等。<br />\n<br />\n除咗保障雙方 , 防止虛假 MeToo 之外 , 只要識得運用「性行為同意書」, 其實仲可以有其他用途"},{"pid":"ac2bdea28d9e7c7ade89f68b7e7d32b24a5ae5df","tid":605757,"uid":58377,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:01:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">當有致命病毒大量傳播，「性行為同意書」就可以用來迅速鎖定傳播範圍</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/25/204755_ae9fbfd1f9bf281bd6848860a3395346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F25%2F204755_ae9fbfd1f9bf281bd6848860a3395346.jpg&h=97ee47d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNBA傳奇球星「魔術手」莊遜 (Magic Johnson) 在 1991 年因為性接觸而患上愛滋病。莊遜有好多性伴侶 , 當中不乏一夜情 , 莊遜自己都唔清楚一夜情對象係咩人 , 所以一直搵唔到感染既源頭<br />\n<br />\n當時傳媒仲爆出更大既新聞 , 引發NBA球壇既恐慌 : <br />\n<br />\n<strong>「莊遜既一眾性伴侶當中，有唔少係同時與其他球星發生過性關係」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民眾一片譁然 , 醫學界擔心愛滋病會廣泛傳播 , 所以就提出要建立<span style=\"color: orange;\">「性伴侶名冊」</span>, 以便係致命病毒大量傳播時 , 用來搵出受感染者 , 甚至追溯出病毒源頭<br />\n<br />\n但因為「性伴侶名冊」會侵犯私隱 , 更會影響性自由既價值觀 , 所以最後就不了了之<br />\n<br />\n「性行為同意書」其實就相當於當時既 性伴侶名冊 , 所以同樣有「迅速鎖定傳染範圍」既用途<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你認為社會需要「性行為同意書」嗎 ? 你對呢個話題有咩意見 ? 大家可以討論一下<br />\n<br />\n<strong>btw 覺得呢篇啱睇既 , 不妨俾小弟一個正評</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec0917a7e2e45a5b8d790a6c4d4ada7e2bae4f0","tid":605757,"uid":58377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:28:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><em>延伸資料：</em></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「性行為同意書」最早的構想是因為 Kobe Bryant ?</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s4.reutersmedia.net/resources/r/?m=02&amp;d=20111217&amp;t=2&amp;i=547900015&amp;r=2011-12-17T022650Z_1_BTRE7BG06ST00_RTROPTP_0_USA-KOBEBRYANT&amp;w=1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.reutersmedia.net%2Fresources%2Fr%2F%3Fm%3D02%26d%3D20111217%26t%3D2%26i%3D547900015%26r%3D2011-12-17T022650Z_1_BTRE7BG06ST00_RTROPTP_0_USA-KOBEBRYANT%26w%3D1280&h=4191b4a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNBA 球星 Kobe Bryant 既自傳式動畫獲得奧斯卡獎之後 , 美國有女權團體出來抗議 , 原因係 Kobe 曾經捲入強姦案<br />\n<br />\n2003年一名19歲少女控告 Kobe 強姦。Kobe承認與少女有發生性行為, 但就堅稱對方係自願。雖然最後雙方達成和解 , 但 Kobe 就從此蒙上污點。<br />\n<br />\n當時洛杉磯既性治療師 Ava Cadell 及律師 Bob Russo 就提出咗「性行為同意書」(Sexual Consent Form) 構想 , 希望藉此避免同類事件發生"},{"pid":"e680a41db429242c23e11c97697275214d1a679c","tid":605757,"uid":130177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"dea95a2c84701a18462de1a053fbe3b115c2ee09","tid":605757,"uid":58377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e680a41db429242c23e11c97697275214d1a679c","tid":605757,"uid":130177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:35:57.000Z","msg":"笑死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:50:10.000Z","msg":"我呢個認真post 黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98df3a7e0ed3adc27fc0a9500dac9a82a0fa9ee6","tid":605